		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Since you're just doing a fangame, it shouldn't really matter.
<br />
<br />However, if you were planning on releasing it on Steam and charging for it, <em>that's</em> when you'd need to worry about permissions. Look at the music in the free and Steam versions of Eversion for an example.

		

